    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Ta darrija Salamans/\nkas tam KUNGAM tabbi ne\npatikke/ un wiꞥſch ne dsinnahs\ngohdigi pehz ta KUNGA/ ka\nwinna Tehws Dahwidg.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Tad ustaitija Salamans\nweenu Augstumu/ Kamofam to\nMoabiteru Elkam/ us to Kalnu\npreekſch Jerusalemes/ un Mole-\nkam to Aumoniteru Elkam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un ta darrija Salamans\nwiꞥſchim fatwahn fweschahm See-\nwahm/ kas faweem Elka-Dee-\nwein tur fwhepinaja un up-\npureja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Tapehz apskaitahg tas\nKUNGS us Salamann/ ka tas\nfawn Sirdi bij nogreestis no ta\nKUNGA Israeta Deewa/ kas\nwinnam diwtkahrt bij parah-\ndijees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un winnam fcho Leetu bij\npawehlejs/ ka tas fwescheim Dee-\nweem pakkat ne statgatu/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Tad fazzija tas KUNG-\nue Salamanu: Tapehz ka ta-\nno tewim notizzis/ un tu ne eff-\nmannu Derribu un mannu Lik-\nkunu fargajs/ ko es tew efmu-\npawehlejs/ tad es teefcham ta-\nWalstibu no tew atrautchu/ un-\ntawam Kalpam dohſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Tomehr tawa Laika eſt-\nne darrischu/ tawa Tehwa Dah-\nwida deht/ no tawa Dehta Roh-\nfas es to atrauschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Tatschu es wiffu Walsti-\nbu ne nemſchu/ weenn Zilti doh-\nfchu es tawam Dehtam/ manna\nKalpa Dahwida deht/ uu Jeru-\nsalemes labbad/ ko es efmu is-\nwehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Un tas KUNGS likfe-\nprett Salamannu weenu Pretti-\nneeku zeltees/ Adadu to Gedomi-\nteri/ tas bija no Rehnixa Dsim-\nmuma eekſch Gedoma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Jo kad Dahwids Gedo-\nma bija/ un Joabs tas Karre-\nLeels-Kungs us augſchu gabje/\ntohs Nokautus aprakt/ kawe-\nwiꞥſch wiﬀius no Wihra Kahr-\ntas eekſch Gedoma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Jo Joabs palikke feſchus\nMehneschus tur ar wiﬀu Isra-\nelu/ kamehr wiꞥſch wiﬀus Wi-\nriskus Gedoma bij isdeldejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Bet Adads bija isbeh-\ndsfs/ un ar winnu zitti Eedo-\nmteru Wihti no fawa Tehwa\nKalpeem/ ka tee us Egipti nahze-\nnn Adad bija mass Puisens.\n"
    }
